'''麥德和'''（{{lang-en|Peter Mak Tak Woh }}），香港商人，前香港電影男演員，其兄是演員[[麥德羅|麥德羅]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hk01.com/電影/490136/靚妹仔-專訪-麥德和曾介紹梁朝偉做臨記-人工唔夠食碗米線|title=【靚妹仔·專訪】麥德和曾介紹梁朝偉做臨記　人工唔夠食碗米線？|access-date=2020-09-23 |work=香港01 |date=2020-07-03 |archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703190344/https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/490136/%E9%9D%9A%E5%A6%B9%E4%BB%94-%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%E6%9B%BE%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9%E6%A2%81%E6%9C%9D%E5%81%89%E5%81%9A%E8%87%A8%E8%A8%98-%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%94%94%E5%A4%A0%E9%A3%9F%E7%A2%97%E7%B1%B3%E7%B7%9A|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==簡歷==
麥德和家有五兄弟一妹<ref>[http://www.kfzimg.com/sw/kfzimg/897/9d79b682472cdb22_b.jpg 麥德和坦言對女孩子沒興趣 在的士高內專跳齋舞] 孔夫子舊書網</ref>，小時跟家人居住在[[香港島|香港島]][[北角|北角]]區<ref>[https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%85&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2FYxWHIw1Z7kdT6XamldIml&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=149&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%85%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%85%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%85%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%85%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%85%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%85%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc 樹欲靜而風不息 麥德羅懷念母親] [[華僑日報|華僑日報]]. 1987-01-17</ref>及[[九龍|九龍]][[馬頭圍邨|馬頭圍邨]]水仙樓。他唸完初中後入讀[[皇家香港警察少年訓練學校|皇家香港警察少年訓練學校]]讀到中五為第7期畢業生。<ref>[https://www.facebook.com/465275270191417/photos/pcb.1677067625678836/1677044215681177/?type=3&theater= 麥德和周身刀] [[吳昊|吳昊]](老花鏡)Facebook圖片. 2017-11-20</ref> 

麥德和早年在[[蘭桂芳|蘭桂芳]][[的士高|的士高]]擔任[[唱片騎師|唱片騎師]]及當過[[龍虎武師|龍虎武師]]與[[錢嘉樂|錢嘉樂]]共事<ref>[https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/490289/%E9%9D%9A%E5%A6%B9%E4%BB%94%E9%87%8D%E6%98%A0-%E5%86%8D%E6%9C%83-%E9%95%B7%E6%A8%82%E8%A1%97peter%E4%BB%94-%E6%B8%A9%E7%A2%A7%E9%9C%9E%E7%AC%91%E6%8C%87-%E4%BB%B2%E4%BF%82%E5%92%81%E6%80%95%E9%86%9C 【靚妹仔重映】再會「長樂街Peter仔」温碧霞笑指：仲係咁怕醜] [[香港01|香港01]]. 2020-06-24</ref>，曾參與1982年電影《[[靚妹仔|靚妹仔]]》拍攝，飾演經典角色「長樂街Peter仔」，之後參加在曼哈頓的士高舉行的「香港熱潮花式舞蹈大賽」與拍擋羅綺綺奪得冠軍<ref>[https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E5%A0%B1&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20all_dc.title%3A%28%22%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%AC%E5%A0%B1%22%29%29%20AND+%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv59H%2FuxqfBwEJN3jQt8uySyp&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=945&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=asc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_filter=dc.publicationdate_dt%3A%5B1980-01-01T00%3A00%3A00Z+TO+1989-12-31T15%3A59%3A59Z%5D 熱潮花式舞蹈大賽 男麥德和女羅綺綺奪標] [[大公報|大公報]]. 1982-08-22（第7頁）</ref><ref>[http://www.kfzimg.com/G06/M00/14/81/p4YBAFufaWOADALuAAMQduiU4Yg064_b.jpg 舞王麥德和、舞后羅綺綺競逐亞洲熱潮舞蹈花式大賽] 電視週刊. 1982</ref>。於1983年便離開香港到內地從事音響生意。同年為[[亞洲電視|亞洲電視]]演出兩套[[查傳誼|查傳誼]]監製的劇集，在拍攝《阿SIR阿SIR》因一場誤會，被警員拔槍喝止打了數拳。<ref>[https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58StS6UNkXpirM9%2B2omKHHT&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=3&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc 鬧市偷拍追逐打鬥鏡頭 警員見狀拔槍喝止 麥德和無端捱數拳] [[工商日報|工商日報]]. 1983-11-15</ref>

