1987年為電影《誓不低頭》往[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]][[檳城|檳城]]拍攝外景時發生嚴重車禍，投資者及武術指導[[小麒麟|小麒麟]]當場喪生，麥德和則受輕傷，該部電影因此胎死腹中。<ref>[https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%8D%BE%E5%B0%91%E6%A3%A0&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BakvA8rFW5EkBDTLIVwZre&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=0&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%8D%BE%E5%B0%91%E6%A3%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%8D%BE%E5%B0%91%E6%A3%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%8D%BE%E5%B0%91%E6%A3%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%8D%BE%E5%B0%91%E6%A3%A0%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%8D%BE%E5%B0%91%E6%A3%A0%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%8D%BE%E5%B0%91%E6%A3%A0%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc 在檳城發生車禍 小麒麟當場喪生 麥德和僥倖只受輕傷] [[華僑日報|華僑日報]]. 1987-04-02</ref><ref>[https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BakvA8rFW5Et5xtxafeQZq&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=16&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E9%BA%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%92%8C%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc 麥德和只傷肩鎖骨 鍾少棠未過危險期] [[華僑日報|華僑日報]]. 1987-04-03</ref>

